                <p>starting to use tools that I've learned in a proper way.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </li>
    <li class="timeline-item">
        <span class="timeline-item-icon | faded-icon"> <Icon name="CarbonShrinkScreenFilled" /> </span>
